.TH opahfirev 1 "Intel Corporation" "Copyright(C) 2015\-2019" "IFSFFCLIRG (Man Page)" 
.SH NAME
opahfirev

.NL

.PP

\fB(Linux)\fR
Scans the system and reports hardware and firmware information about all the HFIs in the system.
.SH Syntax
.NL
opahfirev 
.SH Options
.NL

.TP 10
no option
.NL
Returns information about all of the HFIs in the system.

.TP 10
--help 
.NL
Produces full help text.

.SH Example 
.NL
# opahfirev
.br
######################
.br
phsmpriv07.ph.intel.com - HFI 0000:81:00.0
.br
HFI: hfi1\(ul0
.br
Board: ChipABI 3.0, ChipRev 7.17, SW Compat 3
.br
SN: 0x0063be82
.br
Location:Discrete Socket:1 PCISlot:00 NUMANode:1 HFI0
.br
Bus: Speed 8GT/s, Width x16
.br
GUID: 0011:7501:0163:be82
.br
SiRev: B1 (11)
.br
TMM: 10.4.0.0.146
.br
######################
